Links
=====

Widget gallery > Forms > Auto complete - Add navigation link
------------------------------------------------------------
In the Remark section create a navigation link to the SuggestionPopup.C class.

"You can find several more advanced examples in the Wt distribution directory
examples/feature/suggestionpopup/; in the SuggestionPopup.C class you can
explore different functions."

Widget gallery > Forms > Line/Text editors
------------------------------------------
In the text edit section create an internal link to the pdf renderer
menu/section.
        <a href="#/???">WPdfRenderer</a>
Create the target page for the link.

Widget gallery > Forms > Radio Buttons
--------------------------------------
Create the target menu for the internal link
	<a href="#/events" target="blank">More details on events</a>

Widget gallery > Forms > Button > 'Navigation button' section - enable link
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Create the target page for the internal paths "/navigation" and
"/navigation/anchor" to enable the button link.

